text: Cherry, Harry & Raquel! is a 1969 American action comedy movie directed by Russ Meyer and starring Charles Napier, Larissa Ely, Linda Ashton, Uschi Digard. It was distributed by Panamint Films. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1969 comedy movies Category:1969 action movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Russ Meyer
